data.description: Location! Location! Rarely available two bedroom condo in the most desirable neighborhood in Brookline, the vibrant Audubon Circle/St. Mary's area. This unit boasts a beautifully updated eat-in kitchen with new granite counters and tile back splash that is open to a comfortable living space, perfect for both relaxing and entertaining. Additional features include a separate entrance, new hardwood floors, fresh paint throughout, two very large bedrooms and plenty of full size windows. Exposed brick, high ceilings, generous closet space and IN-UNIT LAUNDRY round out this amazing unit. This association is Pet Friendly and your new home is steps away from the C/D trains, Whole Foods, Down Under Yoga, Fenway Park and plenty of outdoor dining. This condo has a solid rental history and is perfect for an owner occupant or investor. A Must See! All Open House Showings Are By Appointment.
